Rooms.RoomDesc:
This bright, cheerful, cozy, and quiet room at the back of the main inn is decorated with light colored linens, floral wallpaper, and white wicker furniture. Deyett offers a lovely queen bed, a full size en-suite bathroom, and views of the inn's garden. This room does not offer a mini fridge.

CHECK-IN: 3pm-7pm. Pre-paid early/late check-in and late check-out options may be available - please inquire before booking.

Our largest Queen room offers intimacy and elegance, with dark plaid wallpaper and antique furniture. It features a vintage metal sleigh style queen bed, an antique wardrobe, a TV, and mini fridge. A private bath offers a pedestal sink, modern walk-in shower, and antique medicine cabinet. Large windows invite warm southern light and a view of the carriage yard.

CHECK-IN: 3pm-7pm. Pre-paid early/late check-in and late check-out options may be available - please inquire before booking.
